    FLOSS System: <a href="http://picocms.org/">PicoCMS</a>.<br />
    Theme: A COZY mod of <a href="https://gitlab.com/siusoon/soonish/">soonish</a>, that is also modified from <a href="https://github.com/sonst-was/simpleTwo">sonst-was</a>.<br />
    Libre Font: <a href="https://www.velvetyne.fr/fonts/fengardo-neue/">Fengardo Neue</a> & <a href="https://www.velvetyne.fr/fonts/minipax/">MiniPax</a>.
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
